# Rust / Cargo
target/
# Cargo.lock is committed on purpose: soroban-env-host declares an open
# `ed25519-dalek >= 2.0.0` range, and 3.0.0 breaks its build.  The lockfile
# pins 2.2.0 so CI resolves a working dependency set.

